Year: 2014
Platform: h86/h64
Language: Russian / English / Romanian
Activator: Included


System requirements:
Processor: 32-bit (x86) or 64-bit (x64) processor with a clock speed of 1.8 gigahertz (GHz) or higher
Memory: 1 GB or more (GB) (32-bit) or 2 GB or more (64-bit system), memory (RAM)
Video Card: DirectX 9 graphics device with WDDM driver version 1.0 or higher
Free space on HDD: 16 gigabytes (GB) (32-bit) or 20 GB (64-bit system) hard disk space

Description:
Windows 7 is convenient, productive and enjoyable. Better ways to find and manage files, like Jump Lists and a more intuitive view on the taskbar, help to perform familiar tasks faster and easier. Windows 7 provides improved performance and reliability, so your computer will work as you want. With support for 64-bit versions can take full advantage of the latest models of powerful computers and efficient components, such as HomeGroup, Windows Media Center and Windows Touch, will provide new opportunities for controlling the computer and files.

List of editions:
This assembly includes 9 Russian editions, 9 and 9 editions Romanian English editions of Windows 7 SP1 x86 and x64:
Windows 7 Starter (32-bit) Russian / Romanian / English
Windows 7 Home Basic (32-bit) Russian / Romanian / English
Windows 7 Home Premium (32-bit) Russian / Romanian / English
Windows 7 Professional (32-bit) Russian / Romanian / English
Windows 7 Ultimate (32-bit) Russian / Romanian / English

Windows 7 Home Basic (64-bit) Russian / Romanian / English
Windows 7 Home Premium (64-bit) Russian / Romanian / English
Windows 7 Professional (64-bit) Russian / Romanian / English
Windows 7 Ultimate (64-bit) Russian / Romanian / English

List of changes:
Integrated Internet Explorer 11.
Integrated Update on March 2014

Will be automatically installed:
Adobe Flash Player 12 Plugin
Adobe Flash Player 12 ActiveX
Silverlight 5
DirectX 9 June 2010

Additional Information:
If you choose to install Windows 7 Ultimate, then after installation you will be able to switch the interface language from Russian and Romanian to English and back standard means Windows 7 Ultimate. If you have installed any other editor, you can use for this purpose utility Vistalizator, which is available on the desktop &quot;Desktop&quot;.
